data.description: Welcome Home! You feel the warmth of this home as you walk up the covered front porch, enter the foyer, & immediately notice the beautiful custom touches including 10’ ceilings, hardwood floors & tons of natural light. The Great Room is complete w/a fireplace, built ins, large windows & is open to the gourmet kitchen. The features continue w/a double oven, granite countertops & a large pantry. Just off the kitchen is a mudroom w/drop zone leading you to the three car garage. To finish out the main level, there is a bedroom/flex space, full bath, office & dining room. Continue to be impressed as you walk upstairs & find 2 additional bedrooms w/a Jack & Jill bath, additional bedroom w/ensuite bath, laundry & large bonus room, perfect for entertaining. This is all in addition to the primary suite w/trey ceiling & spacious bathroom complete w/separate tub & shower, dual vanity & walk in closet. Located on a cul-de-sac lot in Chesapeake Pointe w/ large flat backyard & trees for privacy.
